1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,496
Danger is not rage.

2
00:00:01,496 --> 00:00:03,150
Rage removes options.

3
00:00:03,150 --> 00:00:10,946
Real capability is
staying calm enough to
see three constructive

4
00:00:10,946 --> 00:00:14,095
Start with ten
phone-free minutes
today.

5
00:00:14,095 --> 00:00:17,324
When the urge to escape
appears, name it.

6
00:00:17,324 --> 00:00:18,505
Do not obey it.

7
00:00:18,505 --> 00:00:23,230
That gap between
impulse and action is
where command begins.
